    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to Sphinxcontrib-applehelp Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>Sphinxcontrib-applehelp</application> package is a
        <application>Sphinx</application> extension which outputs Apple
        help books.
      </para>

      &lfs120_checked;

